      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $(a_n)$ une suite réelle positive.\nOn pose $u_n = \\frac {a_n}{(1+a_1)(1+a_2)\\dots(1+a_n)}$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\((a_n)\\)</span> une suite réelle positive. On pose <span class=\"math inline\">\\(u_n = \\frac {a_n}{(1+a_1)(1+a_2)\\dots(1+a_n)}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "396af758-8cf4-4290-b725-aabbf332891d",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que la série $\\sum u_n$ converge.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que la série <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum u_n\\)</span> converge.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ff015a6a-2641-4875-9320-5d9a100fcf0f",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$u_1 + \\dots + u_n = 1 - \\frac1{(1+a_1)\\dots(1+a_n)} \\le 1$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(u_1 + \\dots + u_n = 1 - \\frac1{(1+a_1)\\dots(1+a_n)} \\le 1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6eaadd45-f559-497f-ba9b-c91399d9e31b",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty u_n$ lorsque $a_n = \\frac 1{\\sqrt n}$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty u_n\\)</span> lorsque <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a_n = \\frac 1{\\sqrt n}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "fa2db27d-f8bb-4547-855d-e2822773682c",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\ln\\bigl((1+a_1)\\dots(1+a_n)\\bigr)\n              = \\sum_{k=1}^n \\ln\\left(1+\\frac1{\\sqrt k}\\right)\n              \\to +\\infty  \\Rightarrow  \\sum u_n = 1$ lorsque $n\\to\\infty$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\ln\\bigl((1+a_1)\\dots(1+a_n)\\bigr)\n              = \\sum_{k=1}^n \\ln\\left(1+\\frac1{\\sqrt k}\\right)\n              \\to +\\infty  \\Rightarrow  \\sum u_n = 1\\)</span> lorsque <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\to\\infty\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
